\Gamma(m+\frac{1}{2}) = \frac{(2n)!\sqrt{\pi}}{4^nn!}
J_{\frac{1}{2}} = \left(\frac{2}{x}\right)^\frac{1}{2}\sum_{n=0}^{\infty}\frac{(-1)^n}{n!\frac{(2(n+1))!\sqrt{\pi}}{4^{n+1}(n+1)!}}\left(\frac{x}{2}\right)^{2n+1}
